To enhance if other requirements:
  --enable-frei0r   ==> Could benefit from adding cross/cairo
                        Generates the following extras libs:
                           lib:lib/frei0r-1/cairoaffineblend.so
                           lib:lib/frei0r-1/cairoblend.so
                           lib:lib/frei0r-1/cairogradient.so
                           lib:lib/frei0r-1/cairoimagegrid.so

Candidates for enablement:
  --enable-ladspa
  --enable-libbs2b 
  --enable-libcdio 
  --enable-libflite 
  --enable-libgme 
  --enable-libgsm 
  --enable-libmysofa      --> https://github.com/hoene/libmysofa
  --enable-libopenmpt 
  --enable-librubberband  --> https://breakfastquay.com/rubberband/
  --enable-libsnappy      --> https://github.com/google/snappy
  --enable-libsrt         --> https://github.com/Haivision/srt
  --enable-libssh 
  --enable-libvidstab     --> https://github.com/georgmartius/vid.stab
  --enable-lv2            --> https://lv2plug.in/
  --enable-omx            --> arch64 specific: to revisit if working for gstreamer
  --enable-pocketsphinx 
  --enable-libiec61883 

Not to be enabled:
  --enable-libxvid 
  --enable-librsvg   ==> Requires gobject-introspection + python + many other dependencies increasing spk size
  --enable-libjack 
  --enable-libpulse 
  --enable-openal 
  --enable-opencl 
